# Structure-First Pipeline (Web Page Builder)

When building pages via `z_workflow/cursor-build-workflow.md`, **compose structure from section patterns** — do not clone a whole reference page.

**New Writer doc?** Read `z_workflow/writer-drop-playbook.md` before Phase 0.

**Writer brief gate:** Zoho **Writer API** only (`web-tool/server/writer-api.js` / Web Page Builder Phase 0). **Never** Chrome MCP or Puppeteer for Writer docs. API auth fail → hard stop; ask user to Sign in with Zoho in the tool.

**Gold-standard reference:** `Reference-Site/agent-reference/` (promoted pages) — correct BEM, section patterns, brief-driven copy.

## What this means

| Do | Do not |
|----|--------|
| Build only sections the writer's doc requires | Copy an entire reference `index.html` and swap copy |
| Pull **per-section** HTML skeleton from `section-index.json` + top matches, or from a `webtemplate` live page (Chrome MCP, one section only) | Copy a reference site's full `style.css` or `script.js`, or inline a webtemplate's whole page |
| Repeat section blocks as many times as the brief needs (e.g. 8 zigzag rows) | Keep reference sections the brief does not mention |
| Extract CSS **only for classes used** on this page | Ship unused reference CSS |
| Include JS **only for behaviors present** (accordion, slick, tabs, sticky) | Copy ads, modals, or unrelated reference JS |
| Use `https://prezohoweb.zoho.com/` + `<!-- TODO -->` for dev handoff | Treat output as production-final |

Each new writer doc → new page composition. Similarity matching picks **section sources**, not a page to duplicate wholesale.

## Phase 0 gate

1. **Writer brief:** Writer API download → `briefs/{slug}.txt` + `.extract.json` (`extraction_method: writer_api`) → `validate:brief` exit 0. API auth fail → stop; do not use Chrome MCP / Puppeteer.
2. Run `node z_workflow/scripts/match-sites.mjs` and record results in `z_workflow/state.json`.
2. Set `similarity.primary_source` to the top-scoring reference folder for **tokens and flavour** — not for blind full-page copy.
3. Build `similarity.source_map`: one entry per **brief section** → reference folder → BEM class → layout style.
4. Use `section-index.json` alternates when the top site lacks a required section type. If still unmatched, pick from `webtemplate/sitemap-categorized.json` by reading each entry's **`sections[]` descriptions** (type + layout, e.g. `split — text left, image right`, `zigzag — alternating text/image rows`). Use `npm run find:webtemplate -- <type> "<layout keyword>"` to shortlist. Fetch only the matched section live via Chrome MCP in Phase 6 **(live marketing pages only — not Writer)**. Tag each `source_map` entry `source_type: "reference" | "webtemplate"`.
5. Set `similarity.structure_mode: "compose"` in `state.json` (not `clone_mode`).

Synthesis is allowed for individual sections with no reference match — use `team-dna.json` + section-index alternates.

## Build steps (mandatory order)

1. **Parse brief** → `sections_required` drives page length and order. Writer doc is the only content source.
2. **Compose `index.html`** section by section:
   - Read the reference section's HTML skeleton (class names, nesting, component shape).
   - Instantiate the pattern once per brief item (hero ×1, FAQ items ×N, zigzag blocks ×N, cards ×N).
   - Inject copy from `z_workflow/briefs/{slug}.txt` only — no invented sections or headings.
3. **Write `style.css`** from scratch for this page:
   - Global typography block at top (per Rulesbook / web-pages-frontend).
   - `:root` tokens from Phase 1 design tokens.
   - Copy **only** the CSS rules needed for classes on this page — from the mapped reference section(s), not the whole reference file.
4. **Write `script.js`** with only behaviors this page uses — copy patterns from reference, trim everything else.
5. **Link** `../../source/zohocustom.css` and `../../source/product.css`. Use `https://prezohoweb.zoho.com/` for all placeholder images, icons, and banner backgrounds.
6. **Nav/footer** — comment placeholders only; team inserts templates separately.

## Section gate (before moving on)

For each section, confirm:

- BEM/classes match the mapped reference section pattern
- Copy comes only from the brief
- Block count matches brief (not reference page count)
- Responsive breakpoints present (1240 · 1080 · 991 · 767 · 565 · 480 · 350)
- `<!-- TODO: replace with final asset -->` on every placeholder image

## Dev handoff intent

Output is a **structured scaffold** for the dev team:

- Semantic HTML + team BEM patterns in place
- Placeholder images and TODO comments flagged
- Nav/footer slots empty
- Devs swap assets, wire nav/footer templates, and polish — structure is already correct

## Before approve

Run `/review` (or checklist in `.cursor/rules/web-pages-frontend.mdc`). **Read `z_workflow/agent-build-gates.md`** — verify CTAs are visible in browser, all Writer pages extracted, composite sections present. Open `index.html` in the browser. Update `z_workflow/state.json` → `phase_6.revise_rounds` on rebuilds.

## Anti-patterns

- ❌ Hiding `.cta-btn` in output without `.page-container .cta-btn.act-btn { display: inline-block }` override
- ❌ Adding `:focus` / `:focus-visible` outline rings on CTAs, tabs, steps, or accordion headers — use `outline: none; box-shadow: none`
- ❌ Tinting `.cta-btn.act-btn` or **See all testimonials** from page `--color-primary` — brand red `#e42527` only (`Rulesbook.md` §2.2.1)
- ❌ Tinting `.zwc-nav-box` testimonial cards from page theme (cyan/violet/teal) — use fixed extracted peach/mint/blue (`Rulesbook.md` §2.2.2)
- ❌ Extracting only page 1 of a multi-page Writer doc
- ❌ Skipping `reported-section` / `testimonials-section` on dashboard-examples landings when brief page ~10 has social proof

- ❌ Using `briefs/*.txt` from a prior session when user provided a fresh Writer URL (re-run Writer API extract)
- ❌ Extracting Writer via Chrome MCP or Puppeteer — **Writer API only**
- ❌ Building when Writer API auth fails without stopping for Zoho re-sign-in in the Web Page Builder
- ❌ Keeping reference sections not in the writer's doc
- ❌ Cloning `output/*` pages as templates (use `section-index.json` + reference site folders)
- ❌ Inventing section class names when `section-index.json` already has a pattern
- ❌ Building nav or footer code
- ❌ Skipping JS for accordion / slick / tabs when those sections are present
- ❌ TOC scrollspy that jumps ahead early — use `scrollY + headerHeight + 60` with **document** offset (`getBoundingClientRect` / jQuery `.offset().top`), never `element.offsetTop` (gold: `output/cloud-analytics/script.js`, `Reference-Site/page-revamp/script.js`, live `cloud-reporting-tools.html`)
- ❌ Skipping `z_workflow/gold-snippets/article-toc-layout.css` on comparison-guide / `.tabsection` builds — copy that snippet (gold page: `output/cloud-analytics`)
- ❌ Skipping `z_workflow/gold-snippets/spreadsheet-reporting-layout.css` on `spreadsheet-reporting-landing` builds — cream cards need `isolation:isolate` + `::before` `#fef8eb` `z-index:0` (never `-1`)
- ❌ Skipping `z_workflow/gold-snippets/database-connector-type-scale.css` on `database-connector-landing` builds — h1 50 · h2 36 · p 17 (never scaffold h1 42 / h2 32 / p 16); gold: `output/sqlite-db-page-draft-2`
- ❌ Skipping `z_workflow/gold-snippets/database-connector-zresrc-cards.css` on `database-connector-landing` — `.zresrc-list` must be BOX cards (35px pad · 12px radius · soft shadow) + `.learn-more-cta`
- ❌ Omitting `<img class="zconnecting-icon">` placeholders on DB-connector key features — live Athena icons are images (sprite/PNG), not text
- ❌ Filling testimonials marquee on `what-is-business-intelligence` — header + See all link only; no `.zwc-nav-box` cards
- ❌ Matching Shopify / SaaS app-connector briefs to `database-connector-landing` because of **Data blending** — use `app-connector-landing` (gold: live `shopify-advanced-analytics.html`)
- ❌ Matching **Mobile Apps** / `ZA BI APP Main Page` / `mobile-apps.html` briefs to `database-connector-landing` because of **Zia Insights** — use `mobile-apps-landing` (gold: live `mobile-apps.html`)
- ❌ Matching **Firebird** / `firebird.html` briefs to Athena `database-connector-landing` — use `firebird-db-landing` (gold: `output/firebird` · snippet `firebird-db-type-scale.css`)
❌ Leaving Firebird `.za-feature-title` at 17px or Athena side-by-side zdashboard titles — centered stack · h2 32 · lead 26/40
- ❌ Skipping ★ Trusted Brands inject on `bi-software-landing` — use `.za-brandsCounts` inject + `gold-snippets/bi-software-trusted-brands-isolation.css`; do not compose live `.trust-section` / `.tbrand-section` when inject is on
- ❌ Leaving hero `item1::before` / `item3::before` / `.banner-arrow` as bare `https://prezohoweb.zoho.com/` — use `banner-before.png`, `banner-beforegraph.svg`, `banner-arrow.svg` under `/sites/zweb/images/analytics/business-intelligence/`
- ❌ Shipping unscoped `.trust-icon { margin: -120px }` with Trusted Brands inject — clips logo marquee (gold: `output/bi-software-3`)
- ❌ Appending Writer “Separate banner for this:” lines inside `.progress-section` / goals accordion — emit sibling `.pre-banner` (gold: `#goals-align-banner` in `output/what-is-business-intelligence-lp-3`)
- ❌ Using testing-3 clip-path / 55% zigzag panels on spreadsheet-reporting landings — use live cream 871×570 cards instead
- ❌ Article TOC without peach `.banner` **inside** `ul#tabs`, or crushed tables — `.table-wrap { overflow-x:auto }` + `.comparison-table-7col` min-width 1200px + `word-break:normal` (gold: `output/cloud-analytics`)
- ❌ Narrow TOC + content starting early — **340px** `.left-tab`, `.cont-sec { margin-left: 100px }`, peach CTA scrolls **with** TOC
- ❌ Putting FAQ / FAQs / `#faqs` in the left-tab TOC — sidebar lists article sections only; FAQ stays as `.faq-section` after `.tabsection` (live `cloud-reporting-tools`)
- ❌ Leaving closing `#conclusion.pre-banner-section` on plain white — use a type from `z_workflow/end-banner-types.json` (assigned in `state.similarity.end_banner`)
- ❌ Reusing the same `blue-shadow-with-texture` closing band on every build — rotate EB-01…EB-08 (webtemplate colour patterns)
- ❌ Placing mid-page/closing red CTAs on plain white `za-bottom-section` — use styled `pre-banner-section` end-banner; mid-cta may be `.bg-white`
- ❌ Zigzag `.dashboard-wrapper` rows without clip-path panels, row spacing (`100px 0` / `margin-bottom: 50px`), or centered image column
